<h3>Tips &amp; Tools</h3>
<p>Congratulations on making the decision to manage your stress! This section is intended to provide you with helpful tips and specific tools to help you succeed with your goals.</p>

<h3>Tools & Strategies for managing your stress:</h3>

<p>Following is a list of common strategies for stress management.</p>

    <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/course">I will attend a stress-management course or support group in the community</a>
    <br><br>
    <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/breaks">I will take regular short relaxation or stretch breaks throughout my day</a>
    <br><br>
   <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/books">I will explore self-help books on stress</a>
    <br><br>
    <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/say-no">I will just say “no” to avoid over-committing myself and set boundaries</a>
    <br><br>
    <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/meditation">I will use meditation or other relaxation techniques to manage my stress</a>
    <br><br>
    <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/set-limits">I will set limits on taking care of others</a>
    <br><br>
    <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/physically-active">I will stay physically active to lower stress</a>
    <br><br>
    <a href="/health-tips/{$data.location}/managing-stress/my-tips-tools/stress-level">I will focus on my stress level and make changes throughout the day</a>

